## <a name="authentication-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="8df23-165">Autentifikācijas notikumi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-165">Authentication events</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-166">Šie diagnostikas datu notikumi tiek apkopoti, kad Office mēģina iegūt autentifikācijas marķieri vai nu nemanāmi vai izmantojot uzvedni.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-166">These diagnostic data events are collected when Office attempts to acquire an authentication token, either silently or through prompting.</span></span>

### <a name="officeandroidmsaguesttoaad"></a><span data-ttu-id="8df23-167">Office.Android.MSAGuestToAAD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-167">Office.Android.MSAGuestToAAD</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-168">Šis notikums palīdz izprast, cik daudziem lietotajiem tiek lūgts norādīt personiskā konta paroli, piekļūstot darba resursiem, jo viņu personiskais konts var būt derīgs darbam ar konta nomnieku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-168">This event helps in understanding how many users are getting prompted for providing personal account password, while accessing work resource, as their personal account could be a valid guest to work account's tenant.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-169">Šie dati palīdz mums saprast, cik daudziem lietotajiem ir jāsaskaras ar atkārtotām pieteikšanās uzvednēm, lai prioritizētu nemanāmu AAD marķieru iegūšanu balstoties uz Microsoft konta SAML (drošības novērtējuma iezīmēšanas valoda) vērtējumu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-169">This data helps us understand how many users are going through the pain of sign in re-prompts to prioritize AAD token acquisition silently based on a Microsoft account SAML (Security Assertion Markup Language) assertion.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-170">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-170">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-171">**Tag** — norāda, ka lietotājs, piekļūstot darba resursam, saņēma pierakstīšanās uzvedni personiskajam kontam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-171">**Tag** - Indicates that user got sign-in prompt for personal account, while accessing work account resource.</span></span>


### <a name="officeidentityfbapromptwin32"></a><span data-ttu-id="8df23-172">Office.Identity.FbaPromptWin32</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-172">Office.Identity.FbaPromptWin32</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-173">Tiek apkopots, kad Office rāda lietotājam uz veidlapām balstītas pierakstīšanās uzvedni.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-173">Collected when Office shows the user a Forms-Based-Auth sign-in prompt.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-174">Kopā ar kluso pilnvaru iegūšanu autentifikācijas uzvednes tiek izmantotas, lai noteiktu, vai lietotājs ir bojātā autentifikācijas stāvoklī, kas lietotājam izraisa būtībā bezsaistes klienta stāvokli, vai sliktākajā gadījumā bojāta autentifikācija var traucēt licences iegūšanu, kā arī izraisīt pilnībā nelietojamu klientu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-174">Along with silent token acquisitions, authentication prompts is used to determine if user is in a broken authentication state which, for the user, results in what is essentially an Offline Client state, or in the worst case, broken authentication may prevent license acquisition and result in a completely unusable client.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-175">Uz veidlapām balstītās autentifikācijas (FBA) pierakstīšanās uzvednes tiek izmantotas dažiem lokāliem autentifikācijas scenārijiem, un parasti mēs vēlamies nodrošināt, ka tā nenotiek, jo visiem vajadzētu lietot moderno autentifikāciju ar FBA saistīto drošības ievainojamību dēļ.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-175">Forms-Based-Auth (FBA) sign-in prompts are used for some on-premises authentication scenarios and typically we want to make sure this isn’t happening, as everyone should be using Modern-Auth because of security vulnerabilities associated with FBA.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-176">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-176">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-177">**AuthScheme** — izmantotā autentifikācijas shēma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-177">**AuthScheme** - the authentication scheme used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-178">**DocumentUrlHash** — šifrēta URL pieprasīšana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-178">**DocumentUrlHash** - an encrypted URL requesting</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-179">**EndTag** — tags, kur FBA veidlapa tiek aizpildīta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-179">**EndTag** - the tag where FBA form is completed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-180">**Flags** — novecojis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-180">**Flags** - Obsolete</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-181">**FlowTag** — tags, kur FBA veidlapa tiek startēta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-181">**FlowTag** - the tag where FBA form is started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-182">**LastError** — atgrieztais kļūdas kods</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-182">**LastError** – the error code returned</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-183">**PromptEndTime** — laiks, kad uzvedne tika beigta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-183">**PromptEndTime** - the time when then prompt ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-184">**PromptStartTime** — laiks, kad uzvedne tiek sākta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-184">**PromptStartTime** - the time when the prompt started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-185">**Result** — vai autentifikācija izdevās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-185">**Result** - whether the authentication succeeded</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-186">**SessionEndTime** — laiks, kad notikuma sesija beidzās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-186">**SessionEndTime** – the time when the event session ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-187">**Timeout** — laiks, kad uzvednei iestājās taimauts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-187">**Timeout** - the time when the prompt timed out</span></span>

### <a name="officeidentitysignoutevent"></a><span data-ttu-id="8df23-188">Office.Identity.SignOutEvent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-188">Office.Identity.SignOutEvent</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-189">Tiek apkopots, kad lietotājs izrakstās no Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-189">Collected when a user signs out of Office.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-190">Zinot, ka lietotājs ir izrakstījies, kļūst iespējams klasificēt citus notikumus, piemēram, uzvednes, kā paredzēts, lai šos notikumus varētu pareizi skaitļot uzticamības/gatavības nosūtīšanai metrikā, kā arī izvairīties no brīdinājumiem vai būvējumu atrites kļūdainā iekārtā, kur lietotājam rodas neparedzētas pierakstīšanās uzvednes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-190">Knowing the user is signed-out makes it possible to classify other events, such as prompts, as expected, so those events can be correctly computed in reliability / ship-readiness metrics and avoid alerting or rolling back builds on the faulty premise that the user is experiencing unexpected sign-in prompts.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-191">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-191">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-192">**FlowEndTime** — laiks, kad izrakstīšanās darbība beidzās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-192">**FlowEndTime** - the time when the sign out action ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-193">**FlowStartTime** — laiks, kad izrakstīšanās darbība sākās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-193">**FlowStartTime** - the time when the sign out action started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-194">**IdentityErrorState** — jebkāds identitātes kļūdas stāvoklis izrakstīšanās laikā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-194">**IdentityErrorState** - any identity error state during sign out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-195">**IdentityHashedUniqueId** — šifrētais identitātes ID, kam tiek veikta izrakstīšanās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-195">**IdentityHashedUniqueId** - the encrypted identity ID being signed out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-196">**IdentityProviderType** — tās identitātes nodrošinātājs, kurai tiek veikta izrakstīšanās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-196">**IdentityProviderType** - the identity provider of the identity being signed out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-197">**IdentityUniqueID** — identitātes ID, kam tiek veikta izrakstīšanās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-197">**IdentityUniqueID** - the identity ID being signed out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-198">**SessionEndTime** — laiks, kad notikuma sesija beidzās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-198">**SessionEndTime** - the time when the event session ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-199">**SignOutUserAction** — norāda, ka lietotājs sāk izrakstīšanās darbību</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-199">**SignOutUserAction** - Indicates the user initiates the sign out action</span></span>

### <a name="officeidentitysspipromptwin32"></a><span data-ttu-id="8df23-200">Office.Identity.SspiPromptWin32</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-200">Office.Identity.SspiPromptWin32</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-201">Tiek apkopots, kad Office rāda lietotājam Windows SSPI pierakstīšanās uzvedni.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-201">Collected when Office shows the user a Windows SSPI sign-in prompt.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8df23-202">Kopā ar kluso pilnvaru iegūšanu autentifikācijas uzvednes nosaka, vai lietotājs ir bojātā autentifikācijas stāvoklī, kas izraisa bezsaistes klienta stāvokli.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-202">Along with silent token acquisitions, authentication prompts determine whether a user is in a broken authentication state, which results in an Offline Client state.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8df23-203">Bojāta autentifikācija var traucēt licences iegūšanu, kā arī izraisīt pilnībā nelietojamu klientu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-203">Broken authentication may prevent license acquisition and result in a completely unusable client.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-204">Windows SSPI uzvednes tiek izmantotas autentifikācijai ar Exchange (pasta sinhronizēšanai), ja lietotāja Exchange resurss nav iestatīts daudzfaktoru autentifikācijai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-204">Windows SSPI prompts are used for authenticating with Exchange (for mail synchronizing) when the user's Exchange resource hasn't been setup for multi-factor authentication.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-205">Šie notikumi kopā ar Office.MATS nosaukumvietas notikumiem tiek izmantoti tālāk norādītajiem mērķiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-205">These events, along with the Office.MATS namespace events, are used for the following purposes:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-206">1.\) Identificēt, vai klienti var sekmīgi iegūt autentifikācijas marķieri vai ir pārgājuši bojātā autentifikācijas stāvoklī.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-206">1\) Identify whether clients can successfully obtain an authentication token or have entered a broken authentication state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-207">2.\) Novērtēt, vai izmaiņas, kas radušās klientā vai pakalpojumos, ir izraisījušas kritisku regresiju lietotāja autentifikācijas pieredzē un uzticamībā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-207">2\) Evaluate whether changes that have occurred on the client or services have resulted in critical regressions in the user's authentication experience and reliability</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-208">3.\) Ja rodas kļūme, šie signāli raida svarīgus kļūmju kodus no atbildīgā komponenta (Office klienta kods, autentifikācijas bibliotēkas vai iestāžu pakalpojumi), ko var izmantot klasificēšanai, diagnostikai un mazināšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-208">3\) When failures occur, these signals emit important failure codes from the responsible component (Office client code, authentication libraries, or authority services) which can be used for triage, diagnosis and mitigation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-209">4.\) Šie signāli nodrošina dažādus nosūtīšanas gatavības un darbspējas pārraugus, kas aktivizē brīdinājumus,lai mūsu inženieri varētu ātri iesaistīties un samazināt laiku kritisko lietotāju bloķēšanas kļūmju mazināšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-209">4\) These signals power various ship readiness and health monitors which fire alerts so our engineers can engage quickly and reduce the time to mitigation of critical user-blocking failures</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-210">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-210">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-211">**AllowSavedCreds** — vai jaunie akreditācijas dati ir pastāvīgi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-211">**AllowSavedCreds** - whether the new credential is persisted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-212">**AuthScheme** — izmantotā autentifikācijas shēma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-212">**AuthScheme** - the authentication scheme used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-213">**CredsSaved** — vai jaunie akreditācijas dati ir saglabāti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-213">**CredsSaved** - whether the new credential is saved</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-214">**DocumentUrlHash** — šifrētā URL pieprasīšana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-214">**DocumentUrlHash** - the encrypted URL requesting</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-215">**EndTag** — tags, kur uzvedne beidzās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-215">**EndTag** - the tag where the prompt ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-216">**NewIdentity**\_ErrorState — vai jaunā identitāte ir derīga</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-216">**NewIdentity**\_ErrorState – whether the new identity is valid</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-217">**NewIdentity\_HashedUniqueId** — šifrētais jaunais identitātes ID pēc uzvednes pabeigšanas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-217">**NewIdentity\_HashedUniqueId** - the encrypted new identity ID after prompt is completed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-218">**NewIdentity\_ProviderType** — jaunais identitātes nodrošinātājs pēc uzvednes pabeigšanas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-218">**NewIdentity\_ProviderType** - the new identity provider after the prompt is completed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-219">**NewIdentity\_UniqueID** — jaunais identitātes ID pēc uzvednes pabeigšanas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-219">**NewIdentity\_UniqueID** - the new identity ID after the prompt is completed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-220">**OutStatus** — vai uzvednes izvade ir derīga</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-220">**OutStatus** - whether the prompt output is valid</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-221">**PromptEndTime** — laiks, kad uzvedne tika beigta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-221">**PromptEndTime** - the time when the prompt ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-222">**PromptFailedTag** — tags, kas norāda SSPI uzvednes kļūmi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-222">**PromptFailedTag** - the tag that indicates SSPI prompt failure</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-223">**PromptFlow** — tags, kas izsauca SSPI uzvedni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-223">**PromptFlow** - the tag that invoked the SSPI prompt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-224">**PromptStartTime** — laiks, kad uzvedne tiek sākta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-224">**PromptStartTime** - the time when the prompt started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-225">**Proxy** — vai tiek izmantots starpniekserveris</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-225">**Proxy** - if proxy is used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-226">**ServerHash** — šifrētā servera adrese</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-226">**ServerHash** - the encrypted server address</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-227">**SessionEndTime** — laiks, kad notikuma sesija beidzās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-227">**SessionEndTime** - the time when the event session ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-228">**Timeout** — laiks, kad uzvednei iestājas taimauts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-228">**Timeout** - the time when the prompt is timed out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-229">**UiMessage** — UI ziņojums uzvednē</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-229">**UiMessage** - the UI message in the prompt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-230">**UserNameHash** — šifrētais lietotājvārds</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-230">**UserNameHash** - the encrypted user name</span></span>

### <a name="officeidentitywin32prompt"></a><span data-ttu-id="8df23-231">Office.Identity.Win32Prompt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-231">Office.Identity.Win32Prompt</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-232">Tiek apkopots, kad Office rāda lietotājam daudzfaktoru autentifikācijas pierakstīšanās uzvedni.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-232">Collected when Office shows the user a multi-factor authentication sign-in prompt.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8df23-233">Kopā ar kluso pilnvaru iegūšanu autentifikācijas uzvednes nosaka, vai lietotājs ir bojātā autentifikācijas stāvoklī, kas izraisa bezsaistes klienta stāvokli.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-233">Along with silent token acquisitions, authentication prompts determine whether a user is in a broken authentication state, which results in an Offline Client state.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8df23-234">Bojāta autentifikācija var traucēt licences iegūšanu, kā arī izraisīt pilnībā nelietojamu klientu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-234">Broken authentication may prevent license acquisition and result in a completely unusable client.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-235">Šie notikumi kopā ar Office.MATS nosaukumvietas notikumiem tiek izmantoti tālāk norādītajiem mērķiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-235">These events, along with the Office.MATS namespace events, are used for the following purposes:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-236">1.\) Identificēt, vai klienti var sekmīgi iegūt autentifikācijas marķieri vai ir pārgājuši bojātā autentifikācijas stāvoklī.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-236">1\) Identify whether clients can successfully obtain an authentication token or have entered in to a broken authentication state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-237">2.\) Novērtēt, vai izmaiņas, kas radušās klientā vai pakalpojumos, ir izraisījušas kritisku regresiju lietotāja autentifikācijas pieredzē un uzticamībā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-237">2\) Evaluate whether changes that have occurred on the client or services have resulted in critical regressions in the user's authentication experience and reliability</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-238">3.\) Ja rodas kļūme, šie signāli raida svarīgus kļūmju kodus no atbildīgā komponenta (Office klienta kods, autentifikācijas bibliotēkas vai iestāžu pakalpojumi), ko var izmantot klasificēšanai, diagnostikai un mazināšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-238">3\) When failures occur, these signals emit important failure codes from the responsible component (Office client code, authentication libraries, or authority services) which can be used for triage, diagnosis and mitigation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-239">4.\) Šie signāli nodrošina dažādus nosūtīšanas gatavības un darbspējas pārraugus, kas aktivizē brīdinājumus,lai mūsu inženieri varētu ātri iesaistīties un samazināt laiku kritisko lietotāju bloķēšanas kļūmju mazināšanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-239">4\) These signals power various ship readiness and health monitors which fire alerts so our engineers can engage quickly and reduce the time to mitigation of critical user-blocking failures.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-240">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-240">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-241">**AdalWAMUsed** — tags, kas norāda rezultātu, ja tiek izmantots ADAL-atop-WAM</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-241">**AdalWAMUsed** – the tag that indicates result if ADAL-atop-WAM is used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-242">**CallTag** — tags, kas norāda pierakstīšanās UI izsaucēju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-242">**CallTag** – the tag that indicates the caller of sign in UI</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-243">**Context** — uzvednes pierakstīšanās konteksts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-243">**Context** - the sign in context for the prompt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-244">**EndTagIdentityProviderRequested** — tags, kur tiek pieprasīts identitātes nodrošinātājs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-244">**EndTagIdentityProviderRequested** - the tag where the identity provider is requested</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-245">**HrdShownTag** — tags, kur tiek rādīts HRD pierakstīšanās dialogs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-245">**HrdShownTag** - the tag where the HRD sign in dialog is shown</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-246">**IdentityProviderResulted** — identitātes nodrošinātāja tips, ko tas pieprasa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-246">**IdentityProviderResulted** - the identity provider type it is requesting</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-247">**IdPFlowTag** — tags, kas norāda identitātes pieprasījuma rezultātu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-247">**IdPFlowTag** - the tag that indicates the identity request result</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-248">**LastLoginDelta** — laika delta no pēdējās sekmīgās pieteikšanās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-248">**LastLoginDelta** - the time delta from last successful login</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-249">**NewIdentity\_ErrorState** — vai identitāte ir derīga pēc uzvednes</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-249">**NewIdentity\_ErrorState** - whether the identity is valid after prompt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-250">**NewIdentity\_ProviderType** — jaunā identitātes nodrošinātāja tips pēc uzvednes</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-250">**NewIdentity\_ProviderType** - the new identity provider type after prompt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-251">**NewIdentity\_UniqueID** — jaunais identitātes ID, kas tiek atgriezts pēc uzvednes</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-251">**NewIdentity\_UniqueID** - the new identity ID returned after prompt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-252">**PromptCorrelation** — uzvednes korelācijas ID diagnostikas mērķim</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-252">**PromptCorrelation** - the prompt correlation ID for diagnostic purpose</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-253">**PromptEndTime** — laiks, kad uzvedne tika beigta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-253">**PromptEndTime** - the time when the prompt ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-254">**PromptStartTime** — laiks, kad uzvedne tiek sākta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-254">**PromptStartTime** – the time when the prompt started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-255">**SessionEndTime** — laiks, kad notikuma sesija beidzās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-255">**SessionEndTime** - the time when the event session ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-256">**ShowUIResult** — rezultāta kods, kas atgriezts no uzvednes UI</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-256">**ShowUIResult** – the result code returned from the prompt UI</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-257">**StartTag** — tags, kur Win32 uzvedne tika sākta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-257">**StartTag** – the tag where Win32 prompt started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-258">**Timeout** — laiks, kad uzvednei iestājas taimauts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-258">**Timeout** - the time when the prompt is timed out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-259">**WasIdentitySignedOut** — vai lietotājs ir izrakstījies</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-259">**WasIdentitySignedOut** - whether the user is signed out</span></span>

### <a name="officematsactionofficewin32-officematsactionofficewinrt"></a><span data-ttu-id="8df23-260">Office.MATS.actionofficewin32, Office.MATS.actionofficewinrt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-260">Office.MATS.actionofficewin32, Office.MATS.actionofficewinrt</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-261">Tālāk norādītais apraksts attiecas gan uz Win32, gan WinRT notikumiem (nosaukums ir atkarīgs no platformas).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-261">The following description applies for both Win32 and WinRT events (the name depends on platform.)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-262">Microsoft autentifikācijas telemetrijas sistēma (MATS) tiek apkopota, kad Office mēģina iegūt autentifikācijas marķieri vai nu nemanāmi vai izmantojot uzvedni.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-262">Microsoft Auth Telemetry System (MATS) is collected when Office attempts to acquire an authentication token, either silently or through prompting.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8df23-263">Ja iegūšanas mēģinājumi neizdodas, tiek iekļauta kļūdas informācija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-263">When acquisition attempts fail, error information is included.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8df23-264">Šie notikumi mūsu lietotājiem sniedz iespēju izvairīties no pāriešanas bojātos autentifikācijas stāvokļos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-264">These events help our users avoid entering broken authentication states by:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-265">1.\) Identificēšana, vai klienti var sekmīgi iegūt autentifikācijas marķieri vai ir pārgājuši bojātā autentifikācijas stāvoklī.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-265">1\) Identifying whether clients can successfully obtain an authentication token or have entered a broken authentication state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-266">2.\) Novērtēt, kad izmaiņas rodas klientā vai pakalpojumos, vai tās izraisa kritisku regresiju lietotāja autentifikācijas pieredzē un uzticamībā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-266">2\) Evaluate when changes occur on the client or services, whether they result in critical regressions in the user's authentication experience and reliability</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-267">3.\) Ja rodas kļūme, šie signāli raida svarīgus kļūmju kodus no atbildīgā komponenta (Office klienta kods, autentifikācijas bibliotēkas vai iestāžu pakalpojumi), ko var izmantot klasificēšanai, diagnostikai un mazināšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-267">3\) When failures occur, these signals emit important failure codes from the responsible component (Office client code, authentication libraries, or authority services) which can be used for triage, diagnosis and mitigation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-268">4.\) Šie signāli nodrošina dažādus nosūtīšanas gatavības un darbspējas pārraugus, kas aktivizē brīdinājumus,lai mūsu inženieri varētu ātri iesaistīties un samazināt laiku kritisko kļūmju mazināšanai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-268">4\) These signals power various ship readiness and health monitors which fire alerts so our engineers can engage quickly and reduce the time to mitigation of critical failures.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-269">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-269">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-270">**Actiontype** — kura autentifikācijas bibliotēka tiek izmantota</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-270">**Actiontype** - Which authentication library is used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-271">**Appaudience** — vai lietojumprogrammas būvējums ir paredzēts iekšējai vai ārējai lietošanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-271">**Appaudience** - Is the app build for internal or external use</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-272">**Appforcedprompt** — vai lietojumprogramma ignorēja kešatmiņu un nodrošināja uzvednes rādīšanu piespiedu kārtā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-272">**Appforcedprompt** - Did the app override cache and force a prompt to be shown</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-273">**Appname** — tās lietojumprogrammas nosaukums, kas veic autentifikāciju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-273">**Appname** - Name of the application doing authentication</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-274">**Appver** — tās lietojumprogrammas versija, kas veic autentifikāciju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-274">**Appver** - Version of the application doing authentication</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-275">**Askedforcreds** — vai lietojumprogramma pieprasīja lietotājam ievadīt akreditācijas datus šai darbībai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-275">**Askedforcreds** - Did the application ask the user to enter credentials for this action</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-276">**Authoutcome** — vai autentifikācijas mēģinājums izdevās, neizdevās vai tika atcelts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-276">**Authoutcome** - Did the authentication attempt succeed, fail, or was canceled</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-277">**Blockingprompt** — vai lietojumprogramma parādīja uzvedni, kur bija nepieciešama lietotāja mijiedarbība</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-277">**Blockingprompt** - Did the application throw a prompt requiring user interaction</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-278">**Correlationid** — GUID, kas tiek izmantots savienošanai ar pakalpojumu datiem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-278">**Correlationid** - GUID used for joining with services data</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-279">**Count** — notikumu skaits apkopojuma gadījumos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-279">**Count** - Count of events in cases of aggregation</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-280">**Data\_accounttype** — patērētāja vai organizācijas konts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-280">**Data\_accounttype** - Consumer or organizational account</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-281">**Devicenetworkstate** — vai lietotājs bija tiešsaistē</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-281">**Devicenetworkstate** - Was the user online</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-282">**Deviceprofiletelemetryid** — anonīmais ierīces ID, kas tika izmantots, lai mērītu ierīces pieredzi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-282">**Deviceprofiletelemetryid** - Anonymous device ID used to measure device experience</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-283">**Duration** — cik ilga bija autentifikācija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-283">**Duration** - How long the authentication took</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-284">**Endtime** — kad autentifikācijas notikums beidzās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-284">**Endtime** - When the authentication event ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-285">**Error** — kļūdas kods, ja autentifikācija neizdevās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-285">**Error** - Error code if the authentication failed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-286">**Errordescription** — īss kļūdas apraksts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-286">**Errordescription** - Brief description of the error</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-287">**Errorsource** — vai kļūda radās pakalpojumā, autentifikācijas bibliotēkā vai lietojumprogrammā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-287">**Errorsource** - Did the error come from service, authentication library, or application</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-288">**Identityservice** — vai tika izsaukts Microsoft pakalpojuma konts (MSA) vai Azure Active Directory (AAD) pakalpojums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-288">**Identityservice** - Was Microsoft Service Account (MSA) or Azure Active Directory (AAD) service invoked</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-289">**Interactiveauthcontainer** — kāda veida uzvedne tika rādīta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-289">**Interactiveauthcontainer** - What type of prompt was shown</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-290">**Issilent** — vai uzvedne tika rādīta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-290">**Issilent** - Was a prompt shown</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-291">**Microsoft**\_**ADAL**\_**adal**\_**version** — Azure Active Directory Authentication Library (ADAL) versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-291">**Microsoft**\_**ADAL**\_**adal**\_**version** - Version of the Azure Active Directory Authentication Library (ADAL)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-292">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_api\_error\_code** — kļūdas kods, ko raidīja autentifikācijas bibliotēka šim autentifikācijas mēģinājumam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-292">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_api\_error\_code** - Error code emitted by authentication library for this authentication attempt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-293">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_api\_id** — šim autentifikācijas mēģinājumam izsauktais API</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-293">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_api\_id** - API invoked for this authentication attempt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-294">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority** — Azure Active Directory tās iestādes URL, kas atbildīga par lietotāja autentifikāciju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-294">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority** – Azure Active Directory authority URL responsible for authenticating the user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-295">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority\_type** — patērētāja/Microsoft pakalpojuma līgums (MSA) attiecībā pret organizāciju/Azure Active Directory (AAD); pašlaik vienmēr AAD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-295">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority\_type** – Consumer / Microsoft Service Agreement (MSA) vs organizational / Azure Active Directory (AAD); currently always AAD</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-296">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority\_validation\_status** — norāda, vai autentifikācija tika pabeigta pakalpojuma pusē</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-296">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority\_validation\_status** – Tells whether authentication completed on the service-side</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-297">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_app** — norāda, vai ADAL autentifikācijai izmantoja starpnieku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-297">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_app** - Tells whether ADAL used a broker for authentication</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-298">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_app\_used** — norāda starpnieka nosaukumu (piemēram, Windows kontu pārvaldība)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-298">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_app\_used** – Tells the name of the broker (e.g., Windows Account Management)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-299">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_version** — norāda starpnieka versiju, ja tas tiek izmantots</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-299">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_version** - Tells the version of the broker if used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-300">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count** — kešatmiņas notikumu skaits, ko ADAL veica, izgūstot marķieri</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-300">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count** - Number of cache events ADAL performed while retrieving token</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-301">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_max** — ja šis signāls tiek apkopots, maksimālais jebkura apkopotā notikuma kešatmiņas notikumu skaits.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-301">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_max** - If this signal is aggregated, max cache events of any one of the aggregated events.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-302">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_min** — ja šis signāls tiek apkopots, minimālais jebkura apkopotā notikuma kešatmiņas notikumu skaits.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-302">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_min** - If this signal is aggregated, min cache events of any one of the aggregated events.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-303">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_sum** — ja šis signāls tiek apkopots, visu apkopoto notikumu kešatmiņas notikumu summa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-303">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_sum** - If this signal is aggregated, sum of the cache events of all the aggregated events.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-304">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_count** — cik reižu API lasīja no diska kešatmiņas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-304">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_count** - How many times the API read from the disk cache.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8df23-305">Spēkā, ja ir bijusi vismaz viena lasīšana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-305">Present if there was at least one read.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-306">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_error\_count** — cik reižu diska kešatmiņas lasīšana neizdevās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-306">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_error\_count** - How many times the disk cache read failed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8df23-307">Ir spēkā, ja ir bijusi vismaz viena kļūme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-307">Is present if there was at least one failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-308">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_last\_error** — ADAL kļūdas kods.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-308">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_last\_error** - ADAL error code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8df23-309">Spēkā, ja ir bijusi vismaz viena lasīšanas kļūme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-309">Present if there was at least one read failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-310">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_last\_system\_error** — sistēmas kļūdas kods.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-310">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_last\_system\_error** - System error code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8df23-311">Ir spēkā, ja ir bijusi vismaz viena lasīšanas kļūme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-311">Is present if there was at least one read failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-312">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_count** — cik reižu API rakstīja diska kešatmiņā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-312">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_count** - How many times the API wrote to the disk cache.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8df23-313">Spēkā, ja ir bijusi vismaz viena rakstīšana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-313">Present if there was at least one write.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-314">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_error\_count** — cik reižu diska kešatmiņas rakstīšana neizdevās.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-314">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_error\_count** - How many times the disk cache-write failed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8df23-315">Spēkā, ja ir bijusi vismaz viena kļūme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-315">Present if there was at least one failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-316">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_last\_error** — ADAL kļūdas kods.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-316">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_last\_error** - ADAL error code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8df23-317">Spēkā, ja ir bijusi vismaz viena rakstīšanas kļūme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-317">Present if there was at least one write failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-318">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_last\_system\_error** — sistēmas kļūdas kods.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-318">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_last\_system\_error** - System error code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8df23-319">Spēkā, ja ir bijusi vismaz viena rakstīšanas kļūme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-319">Present if there was at least one write failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-320">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_client\_id** — jauktais AAD lietojumprogrammas ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-320">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_client\_id** - Hashed AAD app ID</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-321">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_extended\_expires\_on\_setting** — patiess/aplams norāda, vai marķierim ir pagarināts kalpošanas laiks.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-321">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_extended\_expires\_on\_setting** - True/false telling if the token has an extended lifetime.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-322">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_coun**t — HTTP izsaukumu skaits, ko veica ADAL.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-322">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_coun**t - Count of HTTP calls made by ADAL.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-323">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_count\_max** — ja šis signāls ir apkopots, maksimālais HTTP izsaukumu skaits, ko ADAL veic jebkuram apkopotajam notikumam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-323">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_count\_max** - If this signal is aggregated, max HTTP calls made by ADAL of any aggregated event.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-324">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_count\_min** — ja šis signāls ir apkopots, minimālais HTTP izsaukumu skaits, ko ADAL veic jebkuram apkopotajam notikumam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-324">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_count\_min** - If this signal is aggregated, min HTTP calls made by ADAL of any aggregated event.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-325">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_count\_sum** — ja šis signāls ir apkopots, HTTP izsaukumu summa, ko ADAL veic visiem apkopotajiem notikumiem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-325">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_count\_sum** - If this signal is aggregated, sum of the HTTP calls made by ADAL of all the aggregated events.</span></span>

### <a name="onenotesigninssoexternalappsaccountfound"></a><span data-ttu-id="8df23-365">OneNote.SignIn.SSOExternalAppsAccountFound</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-365">OneNote.SignIn.SSOExternalAppsAccountFound</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-369">**AccountType** — reģistrē konta tipu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-369">**AccountType** - Logs the type of account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-370">**ProviderPackageID** — reģistrē tās programmas pakotnes ID, kas nodrošināja šo kontu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-370">**ProviderPackageID** - Logs the package ID of the app that provided this account</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-374">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-374">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

## <a name="click-to-run-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="8df23-382">Click-to-Run notikumi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-382">Click-to-Run events</span></span>

### <a name="officeclicktorunbootstrapper"></a><span data-ttu-id="8df23-383">Office.ClickToRun.Bootstrapper</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-383">Office.ClickToRun.Bootstrapper</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-384">Office iestatīšanas un krājumu dati, kas tiek apkopoti, kad lietotājs palaiž failu Office setup.exe, lai modificētu savus instalētos Office produktus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-384">Office set up and inventory data collected when the user is running Office setup.exe to modify their installed Office products.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8df23-385">Tiek izmantots, lai mērītu pilnas lietotāja uzsāktas Office instalēšanas sekmīgu izpildi/kļūmi, tostarp priekšnoteikumu pārbaudes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-385">Used to measure success / failure of a full user-initiated Office installation including pre-requisite checks.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-386">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-386">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-387">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorCode** — kļūdas kods, ar kuru radās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-387">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorCode** – The error code we failed with</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-388">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorSource** — funkcija, ar kuru radās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-388">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorSource** – The function we failed in</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-389">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_FailingState** — daļa, kas neizdevās boostrapperbootstrapper</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-389">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_FailingState** – The part that we failed in the boostrapperbootstrapper</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-390">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_OExceptionType** — izņēmuma veids, ar kuru radās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-390">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_OExceptionType** – The type of exception we failed with</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-391">**Data\_Culture** — kultūra, ar kuru izmantojam šo exe failu, t.i., en-us</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-391">**Data\_Culture** - the culture we are running this exe with, i.e. en-us</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-392">**Data\_HashedOLSToken** — marķiera sha-256 jaukšanas vērtība, ko OLS pakalpojums mums piešķir</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-392">**Data\_HashedOLSToken** - a sha-256 hash of a token the OLS service gives us</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-393">**Data\_Platform** — x64 vai x86 instalācija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-393">**Data\_Platform** - x64 or x86 install</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-394">**Data\_PrereqFailure\_Type** — priekšnoteikumu kļūme, kāda rodas, t.i., operētājsistēma netiek atbalstīta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-394">**Data\_PrereqFailure\_Type** – The prerequisite failure we hit, i.e. the operating system is not supported</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-395">**Data\_ProductReleaseId** — produkts, ko instalējam, t.i., Office 365 ProPlus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-395">**Data\_ProductReleaseId** - Product we’re installing, i.e. Office 365 ProPlus</span></span>

### <a name="officeclicktoruncorruptioncheck"></a><span data-ttu-id="8df23-396">Office.ClickToRun.CorruptionCheck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-396">Office.ClickToRun.CorruptionCheck</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-397">Office iestatīšanas un krājumu dati, kas tiek apkopoti, kad Click-to-Run klients veic bojājumu pārbaudi, lai nodrošinātu, ka Office binārie faili ir pareizi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-397">Office set up and inventory data collected when Click-to-Run client is running a corruption check to make sure that Office binaries are correct.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8df23-398">Tiek izmantots, lai mērītu Office bināro failu bojājumu un to, kuri binārie faili ir bojāti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-398">Used to measure corruption of Office binaries, and which binaries are corrupt.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-399">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-399">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-400">**Data\_Active —** pašreizējais straumes manifests, ko pārbaudām diskā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-400">**Data\_Active -** The current stream manifest we’re checking on disk</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-401">**Data\_ActivePackages —** kādas pakotnes manifests satur</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-401">**Data\_ActivePackages -** what packages the manifest contains</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-402">**Data\_ActiveVersion —** manifesta versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-402">**Data\_ActiveVersion -** the version of the manifest</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-403">**Data\_AddFileCount —** cik failu pievienojam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-403">**Data\_AddFileCount -** how many files we’re adding</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-404">**Data\_AddFileFiles —** failu, ko pievienojam, paraugs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-404">**Data\_AddFileFiles -** a sample of the files we’re adding</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-405">**Data\_CompressionLevel —** kā faili tiek saspiesti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-405">**Data\_CompressionLevel -** how the files are compressed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-406">**Data\_CorruptionCheckLevel —** cik dziļi meklējam bojājumus, pakāpes</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-406">**Data\_CorruptionCheckLevel -** how deeply we’re checking for corruption, stages</span></span>

### <a name="officeclicktorunmachinemetadata"></a><span data-ttu-id="8df23-439">Office.ClickToRun.MachineMetadata</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-439">Office.ClickToRun.MachineMetadata</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-444">**Data\_OfficeVersion** — versija, kādā sistēma Office ir instalēta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-444">**Data\_OfficeVersion** - The version Office is installed in</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-446">**Data\_SqmMachineID** — unikālais datora ID, ko izmanto Windows SQM Data\_SusClientID- datora Office atjaunināšanas identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-446">**Data\_SqmMachineID** – Unique Machine ID used by Windows SQM Data\_SusClientID- Machine Office update identifier</span></span>

### <a name="officeclicktorunodt"></a><span data-ttu-id="8df23-447">Office.ClickToRun.ODT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-447">Office.ClickToRun.ODT</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-448">Office iestatīšanas un krājumu dati, kas tiek apkopoti, kad IT administrators palaiž Office izvietošanas rīka Click-to-Run failu setup.exe, lai modificētu savu lietotāju instalētos Office produktus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-448">Office set up and inventory data collected when an IT Admin is running the Office Deployment Tool Click-to-Run setup.exe to modify their users’ installed Office products.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8df23-449">Tie tiek izmantoti, lai mērītu pilnas IT administratora uzsāktas Office instalēšanas sekmīgu izpildi/kļūmi, tostarp priekšnoteikumu pārbaudes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-449">It is used to measure success / failure of full IT Admin initiated Office installations including pre-requisite checks.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-450">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-450">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-451">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorCode —** kļūdas kods, ar kuru radās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-451">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorCode-** The error code we failed with</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-452">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorSource —** funkcija, ar kuru radās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-452">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorSource-** The function we failed in</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-453">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_FailingState —** daļa, kas neizdevās boot-strapper</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-453">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_FailingState-** The part that we failed in the boot-strapper</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-454">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_OExceptionType —** izņēmuma veids, ar kuru radās problēmas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-454">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_OExceptionType-** The type of exception we failed with</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-455">**Data\_ConfigurationHost —** resursdators, no kura nācis fails configuration.xml</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-455">**Data\_ConfigurationHost-** The host where the configuration.xml came from</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-456">**Data\_ConfigurationId —** ID, ko iegūstam no faila configuration.xml</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-456">**Data\_ConfigurationId-** The ID we get from a configuration.xml</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-457">**Data\_ConfigurationSource —** no kurienes nācis fails configuration.xml</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-457">**Data\_ConfigurationSource-** We the configuration.xml came from</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-458">**Data\_Culture —** kultūra, ar kuru izmantojam šo exe failu, t.i., en-us</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-458">**Data\_Culture-** the culture we are running this exe with, i.e. en-us</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-459">**Data\_HashedOLSToken —** marķiera sha-256 jaukšanas vērtība, ko OLS pakalpojums mums piešķir</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-459">**Data\_HashedOLSToken-** a sha-256 hash of a token the OLS service gives us</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-460">**Data\_MigrateArchRequest —** vai migrējam lietotāju no x86 uz x64 vai pretēji</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-460">**Data\_MigrateArchRequest-** If we are migrating the user from x86 to x64 or vice-versa</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-461">**Data\_MigrateArchRequestValid —** vai uzskatām, ka migrēšanas pieprasījums ir derīgs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-461">**Data\_MigrateArchRequestValid-** If we believe the migrate request is valid</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-462">**Data\_Platform —** x64 vai x86 instalācija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-462">**Data\_Platform-** x64 or x86 install</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-463">**Data\_PlatformMigratedFrom —** sākuma platforma, t.i., x86</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-463">**Data\_PlatformMigratedFrom-** Starting platform, i.e. x86</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-464">**Data\_PlatformMigratedTo —** beigu platforma, t.i., x64</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-464">**Data\_PlatformMigratedTo-** Ending platform, i.e. x64</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-465">**Data\_PrereqFailure\_Type —** priekšnosacījumu kļūme, kas rodas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-465">**Data\_PrereqFailure\_Type-** The prerequisite failure we hit</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-466">**Data\_ProductReleaseId —** produkts, ko instalējam, t.i., Office 365 ProPlus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-466">**Data\_ProductReleaseId-** Product we’re installing, i.e. Office 365 ProPlus</span></span>

### <a name="officeclicktorunrepomanlogger"></a><span data-ttu-id="8df23-467">Office.ClickToRun.RepomanLogger</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-467">Office.ClickToRun.RepomanLogger</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-468">Ziņo par jaunā Click-to-Run atjauninājumu konveijera statusu (“Repoman”) un par to, vai tas veiksmīgi lejupielādē un instalē Office atjauninājumus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-468">Reports on the status for the new Click-to-Run update pipeline (“Repoman”) and if it successfully downloads and applies Office updates.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-469">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-469">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-470">**ApplySucceeded —** patiess, ja konveijers veiksmīgi lietoja Office atjauninājumu, pretējā gadījumā — aplams.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-470">**ApplySucceeded -** True if the pipeline successfully applied an Office update, false if not.</span></span>
  
  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-471">**DownloadSucceeded —** patiess, ja konveijers veiksmīgi lietoja Office atjauninājumu, pretējā gadījumā — aplams.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-471">**DownloadSucceeded -** True if the pipeline successfully downloaded an Office update, false if not.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-472">**ErrorCode —** pēdējās kļūdas kods, kura radās Click-to-Run Repoman konveijerā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-472">**ErrorCode -** The code of the last error that occurred in the Click-to-Run Repoman pipeline.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-473">**ErrorDetails —** papildu informācija par kļūdu, kura radās Click-to-Run Repoman konveijerā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-473">**ErrorDetails -**  Additional error details of the last error that occurred in the Click-to-Run Repoman pipeline.</span></span>
 
  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-474">**ErrorMessage —** pēdējās kļūdas ziņa, kura radās Click-to-Run Repoman konveijerā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-474">**ErrorMessage -** The message of the last error that occurred in the Click-to-Run Repoman pipeline.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-475">**OpenStreamSessionSucceeded —** patiess, ja konveijerā veiksmīgi tiek radīta sesija Office atjauninājuma straumēšanai, pretējā gadījumā — aplams.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-475">**OpenStreamSessionSucceeded -** True if the pipeline successfully creates a session for streaming an Office update, false if not.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-476">**RepomanErrorMessage —** kļūdas ziņojums, kurš saņemts no repoman.dll.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-476">**RepomanErrorMessage -** The error message received from the repoman.dll.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-485">**Data\_16\_SourceType —** kur Office 16 avots atrodas, t.i., CDN vai lokāls</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-485">**Data\_16\_SourceType -** Where the Office 16 source is located i.e. CDN or Local</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-486">**Data\_16\_UpdatesEnabled —** ja Office 16 atjauninājumi ir iespējoti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-486">**Data\_16\_UpdatesEnabled -** If Office 16 updates are enabled</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-487">**Data\_16\_UpdateVersion —** uz kādu Office 16 versiju veicam atjaunināšanu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-487">**Data\_16\_UpdateVersion -** What version of Office 16 we’re updating to</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-1491">Atskaites par darbībām, kas lasa atzīmēto ievadi no .exe faila iegultā paraksta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-1491">Reports on the action that reads tagged input from the exe's embedded signature.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="8df23-1492">Šī ir nepierādīta koncepcija, kuru iepriekšējā programmas setup.exe versija neimplementēja, un uz to mēs paļaujamies, lai pārnestu lietotāja produkta/valodas/bitu skaita izvēles no tīmekļa lapas uz iekšējo procesu programmā setup.exe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-1492">This is an unproven concept the previous iteration of setup.exe did not implement, and is what we're relying on to carry the user's product/language/bitness choices from web page to in-process within setup.exe.</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-1493">**ErrorCode —** vesels skaitlis, kas saistīts ar neapstrādātu izņēmumu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-1493">**ErrorCode –**   Integer number associated with an unhandled exception</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-1511">**IsC2RServiceRunning —** Būla karodziņš, kas norāda, vai modernā C2R klienta lokālā datora pakalpojums ierīcē ir ieslēgts un darbojas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-1511">**IsC2RServiceRunning –** Boolean flag that indicates whether a modern C2R Client's local machine service is up and running on the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-1518">**Origin —** virknes vērtība, kas norāda, kura no atbalstītajām izcelsmes vietām (Puertoriko [PR], Singapūra [SG], Dublina [DB]) ir jāizmanto sākotnējai instalācijas straumēšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-1518">**Origin –**  String value telling us which of the supported origins (Puerto Rico [PR], Singapore [SG], Dublin [DB]) should be used for initial installation streaming</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-1538">**DeliveryMechanism —** “FFNRoot” GUID, kas izvilkts no versijas deskriptora XML faila (apzīmogots ar RDX), kurš norāda, no kuras auditorijas/kanāla ir nācis būvējuma avots</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-1538">**DeliveryMechanism –**   The "FFNRoot" guid extracted from the Version Descriptor XML (stamped by RDX), which tells us which audience/channel the build source came from</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-1544">**ExitCode —** vesela skaitļa vērtība, kas saistīta ar sāknēšanas programmas izpildes fāzes darbības rezultātu, norādot sekmes vai konkrētus kļūmju tipus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-1544">**ExitCode –**    Integer value associated with the result of running the Execute phase of the bootstrapper, indicating success vs. specific types of failure</span></span>

### <a name="officeserviceabilitymanagerinventoryaddonheartbeat"></a><span data-ttu-id="8df23-1550">Office.ServiceabilityManager.InventoryAddon.Heartbeat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-1550">Office.ServiceabilityManager.InventoryAddon.Heartbeat</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-1551">Šis notikums tiek izmantots, lai iegūtu standarta metadatus par katru inventāra pievienojumprogrammas darbību, kas ir daļa no tehniskās apkopes pārvaldnieka un tiek izmantota Office informācijas uzskaitei datoros un ierīcēs, kurām administrators to ir iespējojis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-1551">This event is used to acquire standard metadata on each run of the Inventory add-on, which is part of the Office Serviceability Manager and is used for inventory Office information on those machines for which an IT admin has opted in.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8df23-1552">Šeit īpaši interesanti sesijas ID metadati, kas tiek izmantoti, lai izveidotu saiti uz citiem datiem, kas ir saglabāti katra nomnieka mākoņa pakalpojumā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-1552">The metadata of specific interest here is the session ID, and it is used for linking to other data stored within a per-tenant cloud service.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-1553">Šis notikums nesatur ekstra laukus, jo saistoši ir tikai metadati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-1553">This event contains no extra fields since only the metadata is relevant.</span></span>

### <a name="officeserviceabilitymanagerinventoryaddonresults"></a><span data-ttu-id="8df23-1554">Office.ServiceabilityManager.InventoryAddon.Results</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-1554">Office.ServiceabilityManager.InventoryAddon.Results</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-1555">Šis notikums tiek reģistrēts, kad izsaukums uz tīmekļa pakalpojumu, kas veikts, izmantojot noklikšķināt, lai palaistu funkcionālo darbību pievienojumprogrammu, tiek pabeigts, neatkarīgi no tā, vai tas ir sekmīgs vai nē.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-1555">This event is logged when the call to the webservice made within the Click-to-Run Serviceability Manager Inventory add-on completes, irrespective of whether it succeeds or fails.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8df23-1556">Tā būtībā ir pēdējā operācija pievienojumprogrammā, lai izsekotu kopējo darbības statusu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-1556">This is essentially the last operation within the add-on to track the overall operation status.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-1557">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-1557">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="8df23-1558">**WebCallSource** — uzskaitījuma vērtība (norādīta kā vesels skaitlis), kas norāda, kāda ir apkalpojamības pārvaldnieka pievienojumprogramma, kas bija zvana avots:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-1558">**WebCallSource** - An enumeration value (specified as an integer) indicating the Serviceability Manager add-on that was the source of the call:</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-1559">Krājumu saraksts: 0</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-1559">Inventory: 0</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-1560">Krājumu konfigurācija: 1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-1560">Inventory Configuration: 1</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-1565">Šis notikums tiek reģistrēts katru reizi, kad zvans uz tīmekļa pakalpojumu, kas izveidots, izmantojot noklikšķiniet, lai palaistu pievienojumprogrammu nav sekmīgs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-1565">This event is logged whenever a call to a webservice made within a Click-to-Run Serviceability Manager add-on fails.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-1567">**Pievienojumprogramma** — noklikšķināt, lai palaistu tehniskās apkopes pārvaldnieka pievienojumprogramma, no kuras tīmekļa pakalpojuma zvans tika veikts.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-1567">**Add-on** - The Click-to-Run Serviceability Manager add-on from which the webservice call was made.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8df23-1568">Tam var būt vērtības, piemēram, krājums, pārvaldāmība utt., kas kodēta kā skaitliska vērtība.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-1568">This can have values like inventory, manageability, etc. encoded as a numeric value.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-1569">**Korelācijas ID** — nejauši ģenerētu GUID, kas raksturīgs pašreizējai instancei, kas tiek nosūtīta tīmekļa pakalpojumam, lai saistītu zvanus starp klientu un serveri.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-1569">**Correlation ID** - A randomly generated GUID specific to the current instance that is sent to the webservice to correlate calls between the client and the server.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-1570">**Result** — skaitliska kļūdas kodu informācija, ko atgriezis Office tīmekļa pakalpojumu zvanu API.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-1570">**ErrorInfo** - Numeric error code information returned by the Office webservice call APIs.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-1571">**Funkcija** — funkcija kodā, no kura ir noticis pašreizējais zvans.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-1571">**Function** - The function in the code from which the current call occurred.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-1572">**Statusa** — HTTP statusa kods, ko atgriezis zvans uz tīmekļa pakalpojumu, piemēram, 404, 500 utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-1572">**Status** - The HTTP status code returned by the call to the webservice, e.g. 404, 500, etc.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-1589">Šis pasākums palīdz analizēt produktu lietojuma un veiktspējas rādītāju apjomu (piemēram, avārijas, uzkāršanos) lietotāju vai ierīču apakškopā, kura drīkst izmantot līdzekli, nodrošinot pareizu produkta darbību.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-1589">This event helps scope analysis of product usage and performance metrics (such as crashes, hangs, etc.) to the subset of users or devices that are eligible to use the feature, thereby helping ensure that the product is working properly.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-1600">Tas tiek izmantots, lai noteiktu, vai lietotājs ir piemērotā stāvoklī, kas tiek izmantota sistēmas darbspējai un diagnostikas mērķiem, ja lietotājs ziņo par problēmu savā datorā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-1600">It is used to detect if the user is in a good state or not, used for system health and used for diagnostic purposes if a user reports an issue with their machine</span></span>
