- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-2041">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** — tīkla tips (Wi-Fi, vadu, nezināms)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-2041">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** - The type of network (Wi-Fi, Wired, Unknown)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-2042">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** — operētājsistēmas versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-2042">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** - The version of the Operating System</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-2043">**Event_ReceivedTime** — laiks, kad tika saņemta telemetrija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-2043">**Event_ReceivedTime** - The time at which telemetry was received</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-2044">**EventInfo_Name** — reģistrējamā telemetrijas notikuma nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-2044">**EventInfo_Name** - The name of the telemetry event being logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-2045">**EventInfo_Time** — laiks, kad notika reģistrētais notikums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-2045">**EventInfo_Time** - The time at which the logged event took place</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-2047">**Payload** — ietver ID, kas identificē vienu atjaunināšanas darbību, un klonēšanas procesa laikā ziņoto starpniekservera kļūdu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-2047">**Payload** - Contains an ID to identify a single update activity, and Proxy Error reported during cloning process.</span></span>

### <a name="controller_alertmanager_reinstallresponse"></a><span data-ttu-id="8df23-2093">controller_alertmanager_reinstallresponse</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-2093">controller_alertmanager_reinstallresponse</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-2103">**DeviceInfo_Model** — ierīces aparatūras modelis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-2103">**DeviceInfo_Model** - The Hardware Model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-4875">**App** — programmas process, kas sūta notikumu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-4875">**App** - The application process sending the event</span></span>

### <a name="webservices_silentupdate"></a><span data-ttu-id="8df23-5445">webservices_silentupdate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5445">webservices_silentupdate</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-5446">Reģistrējam pieprasījumus, lai pārbaudītu, vai nav piespiedu atjauninājumu lietošanas kārtulu, t.i., vai lietotājam no būvējuma N nav jāpāriet uz būvējumu N+1, jo pastāv kāda liela problēma.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5446">We log requests to check for any "force update" applicability rules, i.e. we must take a user from build N to build N+1 due to some major issue.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5447">Šis notikums tiek izmantots, lai nodrošinātu paredzēto atjaunināšanas procesa darbību un lai palīdzētu novērst kļūdas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5447">We use this event for ensuring the update process works as expected and to help troubleshoot errors.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5451">**AppVersionLong** — programmas versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5451">**AppVersionLong** - The application Version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5452">**Channel** — auditorijas preference</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5452">**Channel** - The preference for audience</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5453">**Device_NetworkCountry** — ierīces valsts/reģions (atbilstoši IP adresei)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5453">**Device_NetworkCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5454">**DeviceID** — ierīces identifikators</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5454">**DeviceID** - The device identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5455">**DeviceInfo_Model** — ierīces aparatūras modelis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5455">**DeviceInfo_Model** - The Hardware Model of the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5456">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** — tīkla tips (Wi-Fi, vadu, nezināms)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5456">**DeviceInfo_NetworkType** - The type of network (Wi-Fi, Wired, Unknown)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5457">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** — operētājsistēmas versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5457">**DeviceInfo_OsBuild** - The Version of the Operating System</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5458">**Event_ReceivedTime** — laiks, kad tika saņemta telemetrija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5458">**Event_ReceivedTime** - The time at which telemetry was received</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5459">**EventInfo_Name** — reģistrējamā telemetrijas notikuma nosaukums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5459">**EventInfo_Name** - The name of the telemetry event being logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5460">**EventInfo_Time** — laiks, kad notika reģistrētais notikums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5460">**EventInfo_Time** - The time at which the logged event took place</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5461">**HowTocheck** — pārbaudes, vai nav atjauninājumu, preference</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5461">**HowTocheck** - The preference for checking of updates</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5462">**Payload** — satur pieprasījuma ID, programmas nosaukumu, atbildes laiku un/vai statusa kodu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5462">**Payload** - Contains request ID, application name, response time and/or status code.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5463">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** — ierīces valsts/reģions (atbilstoši IP adresei)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5463">**PipelineInfo_ClientCountry** - The device country (based on IP address)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5464">**PipelineInfo_ClientIp** — IP adreses pirmie 3 okteti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5464">**PipelineInfo_ClientIp** - The first 3 octets of the IP address</span></span>

## <a name="onenote-sync-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="8df23-5487">OneNote sinhronizācijas notikumi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5487">OneNote sync events</span></span>

### <a name="officeonenotestoragenotebooksyncresult"></a><span data-ttu-id="8df23-5488">Office.OneNote.Storage.NotebookSyncResult</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5488">Office.OneNote.Storage.NotebookSyncResult</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="8df23-5489">Šis notikums reģistrē piezīmju grāmatiņas sinhronizācijas rezultātu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5489">This event logs notebook sync result.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5490">Tas tiek lietots, lai, aprēķinot OneNote sinhronizācijas vērtējumu, noteiktu, cik daudz ir unikālu sinhronizācijas mērķu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5490">It is used for figuring out how many unique sync targets when calculating OneNote sync score.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="8df23-5491">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5491">The following fields are collected</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5492">**CachedError_Code**A— numurēts vai burtciparu kods, kas tiek lietots, lai noteiktu kešatmiņā saglabātās kļūdas raksturu un/vai to, kāpēc tā radās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5492">**CachedError_Code** - a numbered or alphanumeric code used to determine the nature of the cached error, and/or why it occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5493">**CachedError_Description** — kešatmiņā saglabātās kļūdas apraksts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5493">**CachedError_Description** – a description of the cached error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5494">**CachedError_Tag** — norāda, kur kodā rodas kešatmiņā saglabātā kļūda</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5494">**CachedError_Tag** – indicate where in the code throws the cached error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5495">**CachedError_Type** — kešatmiņā saglabātās kļūdas tips, piemēram, Win32Error u.tml.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5495">**CachedError_Type** – the type of the cached error, e.g. Win32Error, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5496">**ExecutionTime** — laiks milisekundēs, kas bija nepieciešams, lai replicētu piezīmju grāmatiņu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5496">**ExecutionTime** – time in milliseconds taken to replicate the notebook</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5497">**Gosid** — globālais objektu telpas ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5497">**Gosid** – global object space ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5498">**IdentityType** — identitātes tips, piemēram, Windows Live, organizācijas ID utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5498">**IdentityType** – identity type, e.g. Windows Live, Org ID, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5499">**InitialReplicationInSession** — norāda, vai šī replicēšana ir pirmā piezīmju grāmatiņas replicēšana pēc atvēršanas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5499">**InitialReplicationInSession** – is this replication the first notebook replication after open or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5500">**IsBackgroundSync** — norāda, vai tā ir fona sinhronizācija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5500">**IsBackgroundSync** – is this a background sync or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5501">**IsCachedErrorSuppressed** — norāda, vai kešatmiņā saglabātā kļūda tiek apspiesta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5501">**IsCachedErrorSuppressed** – is the cached error suppressed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5502">**IsCachedErrorUnexpected** — norāda, vai kešatmiņā saglabātā kļūda ir neparedzēta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5502">**IsCachedErrorUnexpected** – is the cached error unexpected or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5503">**IsNotebookErrorSuppressed** — norāda, vai piezīmju grāmatiņas līmeņa sinhronizācijas kļūda tiek apspiesta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5503">**IsNotebookErrorSuppressed** – is the notebook level sync error suppressed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5504">**IsNotebookErrorUnexpected** — norāda, vai piezīmju grāmatiņas līmeņa sinhronizācijas kļūda ir neparedzēta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5504">**IsNotebookErrorUnexpected** – is the notebook level sync error unexpected or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5505">**IsSectionErrorSuppressed** — norāda, vai sadaļu sinhronizācijas kļūdas tiek apspiestas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5505">**IsSectionErrorSuppressed** – is the section sync error suppressed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5506">**IsSectionErrorUnexpected** — norāda, vai sadaļas sinhronizācijas kļūda bija paredzēta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5506">**IsSectionErrorUnexpected** – is the section sync error unexpected or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5507">**IsUsingRealtimeSync** — norāda, vai piezīmju grāmatiņas sinhronizēšana notiek, izmantojot moderno lapas satura sinhronizāciju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5507">**IsUsingRealtimeSync** – is the notebook sync using modern page content sync or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5508">**LastAttemptedSync** — laikspiedols, kad piezīmju grāmatiņu tika mēģināts sinhronizēt iepriekšējo reizi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5508">**LastAttemptedSync** – timestamp when the notebook was attempted to be synced last time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5509">**LastBackgroundSync** — laikspiedols, kad notika pēdējais mēģinājums veikt sinhronizāciju fona režīmā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5509">**LastBackgroundSync** – timestamp when the latest background sync was attempted</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5510">**LastNotebookViewedDate** — datums, kad piezīmju grāmatiņa pēdējoreiz tika skatīta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5510">**LastNotebookViewedDate** – the date when the notebook was last viewed</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5511">**LastSuccessfulSync** — laikspiedols, kad piezīmju grāmatiņa iepriekš sekmīgi sinhronizēta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5511">**LastSuccessfulSync** – timestamp when the notebook successfully synced before</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5512">**NeedToRestartBecauseOfInconsistencies** — norāda, vai sinhronizācija ir jārestartē, jo pastāv nekonsekvences</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5512">**NeedToRestartBecauseOfInconsistencies** – does the sync need to restart because of inconsistencies or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5513">**NotebookErrorCode** — piezīmju grāmatiņas līmeņa sinhronizācijas kļūdas kods, kas saglabāts piezīmju grāmatiņas diagrammas apgabalā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5513">**NotebookErrorCode** – notebook level sync error code saved on notebook graph space</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5514">**NotebookId** — piezīmju grāmatiņas ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5514">**NotebookId** – notebook ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5515">**NotebookType** — piezīmju grāmatiņas tips</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5515">**NotebookType** – notebook type</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5516">**ReplicatingAgainBecauseOfInconsistencies** — norāda, vai sinhronizācija tiek restartēta nekonsekvenču dēļ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5516">**ReplicatingAgainBecauseOfInconsistencies** – does the sync restart because of inconsistencies or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5517">**SectionError_Code** — numurēts vai burtciparu kods, kas tiek lietots, lai noteiktu sadaļas sinhronizācijas kļūdas raksturu un/vai to, kāpēc tā radās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5517">**SectionError_Code** – a numbered or alphanumeric code used to determine the nature of the section sync error, and/or why it occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5518">**SectionError_Description** — sadaļas sinhronizācijas kļūdas apraksts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5518">**SectionError_Description** – a description of the section sync error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5522">**SyncDestinationType** — sinhronizācijas galamērķa tips, t.i., OneDrive vai SharePoint Online</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5522">**SyncDestinationType** – sync destination type, i.e. OneDrive or SharePoint Online</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5523">**SyncId** — katrai piezīmju grāmatiņas sinhronizācijai unikāls numurs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5523">**SyncId** – a number unique to each notebook sync</span></span>

### <a name="officeonenotestoragerealtimewebsocketsessioninfo"></a><span data-ttu-id="8df23-5529">Office.OneNote.Storage.RealTime.WebSocketSessionInfo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5529">Office.OneNote.Storage.RealTime.WebSocketSessionInfo</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="8df23-5530">Šis notikums reģistrē WebSocket sinhronizācijas rezultātu gan OneNote modernā lapas satura sinhronizācijai, gan modernās hierarhijas sinhronizācijai. Tas tiek lietots, lai, aprēķinot OneNote sinhronizācijas vērtējumu, noteiktu, cik daudz ir unikālu sinhronizācijas mērķu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5530">This event logs WebSocket sync result for both OneNote modern page content sync modern hierarchy sync. It is used for figuring out how many unique sync targets when calculating OneNote sync score.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5531">Tas tiek izmantots arī OneNote modernās sinhronizācijas veiktspējas informācijas paneļa vajadzībām.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5531">It is also used for OneNote modern sync performance dashboard.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="8df23-5532">Tiek apkopoti šādi lauki:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5532">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5533">**CloseReason** — WebSocket aizvēršanas iemesls, piemēram, anormāla aizvēršana utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5533">**CloseReason** - WebSocket close reason, e.g. Abnormal close, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5534">**DataIsFreshCount** — sekmīgo atgādāšanas pieprasījumu skaits WebSocket sesijā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5534">**DataIsFreshCount** - number of successful pull requests in the WebSocket session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5535">**DeviceSessionId** — ierīces sesijas ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5535">**DeviceSessionId** - Device session ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5536">**DownloadCount** — lejupielāžu skaits WebSocket sesijā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5536">**DownloadCount** - number of downloads in the WebSocket session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5537">**Error** — tas pamatā ir Exception_Type+Exception_Description+Exception_Code+Exception_Tag</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5537">**Error** - is basically Exception_Type + Exception_Description + Exception_Code + Exception_Tag</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5538">**Exception_Code** — numurēts vai burtciparu kods, kas tiek lietots, lai noteiktu kļūdas raksturu un/vai to, kāpēc tā radās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5538">**Exception_Code** - a numbered or alphanumeric code used to determine the nature of an error, and/or why it occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5539">**Exception_Description** — kļūdas apraksts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5539">**Exception_Description** - a description of the error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5540">**Exception_Tag** — norāda, kur kodā rodas kļūda</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5540">**Exception_Tag** - indicate where in the code throws the error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5541">**Exception_Type** — kļūdas tips, piemēram, Win32Error u.tml.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5541">**Exception_Type** - the type of the error, e.g. Win32Error, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5542">**FirstUpdateSize** — pirmā atjaunināšanas ziņojuma garums</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5542">**FirstUpdateSize** - first update message length</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5543">**HasError** — norāda, vai WebSocket sesijas laikā radās kļūda</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5543">**HasError** - whether there is an error during the WebSocket session</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5544">**IsEducationNotebook** — norāda, vai pašreizējā piezīmju grāmatiņa ir piezīmju grāmatiņa izglītības iestādēm</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5544">**IsEducationNotebook** - Is the current notebook education notebook or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5545">**IsHierarchyResource** — norāda, vai pašreizējais resurss ir lapa vai sadaļa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5545">**IsHierarchyResource** - Is the current resource a page or a section</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5546">**NotebookId** — OneNote piezīmju grāmatiņas ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5546">**NotebookId** - OneNote notebook ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5547">**OperationWithError** — kuras operācijas laikā notika kļūda, piemēram, WebSocket.Close, WebSocket.Open u.tml.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5547">**OperationWithError** - in which operation did the error happen, e.g. WebSocket.Close, WebSocket.Open, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5548">**ResourceId** — OneNote lapas vai sadaļas resursa ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5548">**ResourceId** - OneNote page or section resource ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5549">**SectionId** — OneNote sadaļas ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5549">**SectionId** - OneNote section ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5550">**ServerSessionId** — sesijas ID, kas tiek izmantota savstarpējai WebSocket pieprasījuma un onenote.com saistīšanai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5550">**ServerSessionId** - session ID used to correlate WebSocket request to onenote.com</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5551">**SessionDurationInMs** — WebSocket sesijas ilgums milisekundēs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5551">**SessionDurationInMs** - the duration in milliseconds of the WebSocket session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5552">**TenantId** — SharePoint nomnieka ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5552">**TenantId** - SharePoint tenant ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5553">**TimeToFirstUpdateInMs** — laiks milisekundēs, kas bija nepieciešams, lai saņemtu pirmo atjauninājumu no servera puses pēc tam, kad tika izveidota WebSocket sesija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5553">**TimeToFirstUpdateInMs** - time in milliseconds taken to receive first update from the server side after the WebSocket session is established</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5554">**UploadAckCount** — augšupielādes apstiprinājumu skaits WebSocket sesijā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5554">**UploadAckCount** - number of acknowledges for upload in the WebSocket session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5555">**Web URL** — PII notīrītais tīmekļa vietrādis URL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5555">**WebUrl** - PII scrubbed web URL</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5565">**ErrorLast** — pēdējās radušās kļūdas kods</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5565">**ErrorLast** - the error code of last seen error</span></span>

### <a name="officeonenotestoragesyncscore"></a><span data-ttu-id="8df23-5588">Office.OneNote.Storage.SyncScore</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5588">Office.OneNote.Storage.SyncScore</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="8df23-5589">Šis notikums reģistrē visus lietotājiem redzamos negatīvos sinhronizācijas iespēju apstākļus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5589">This event logs all negative factors in sync experience that are visible to users.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5590">Tas tiek lietots, lai aprēķinātu OneNote sinhronizācijas vērtējumu, kas ir kritisks rādītājs, novērtējot OneNote lietotāju sinhronizācijas iespējas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5590">It is used to calculate OneNote sync score, which is a critical metric to evaluate OneNote users' sync experience.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="8df23-5591">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5591">The following fields are collected</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5592">**AutoShowSyncStatus** — norāda, vai sinhronizācijas statuss tiek rādīts automātiski</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5592">**AutoShowSyncStatus** - whether sync status is auto shown or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5593">**Cause** — kas izraisīja OneNote lapu/sadaļu pārvietošanu uz nesakārtotām sadaļām</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5593">**Cause** - what caused OneNote pages/sections moved to misplaced sections</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5594">**Context** — uzskaitījums kategorizē, ko lietotājs cenšas veikt, piemēram, sadaļas pārdēvēšana, piezīmju grāmatiņas atkārtota atvēršana utt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5594">**Context** - an enum categorizes what user is trying to do, e.g. rename a section, reopen a notebook, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5595">**Error_Code** — numurēts vai burtciparu kods, kas tiek lietots, lai noteiktu kļūdas raksturu un/vai to, kāpēc tā radās</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5595">**Error_Code** - a numbered or alphanumeric code used to determine the nature of an error, and/or why it occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5596">**Error_Description** — kļūdas apraksts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5596">**Error_Description** - a description of the error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5597">**Error_Tag** — norāda, kur kodā rodas kļūda</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5597">**Error_Tag** - indicate where in the code throws the error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5598">**Error_Type** — kļūdas tips, piemēram, Win32Error u.tml.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5598">**Error_Type** - the type of the error, e.g. Win32Error, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8df23-5599">**ErrorText** — kļūdas teksts, kas redzams lietotāja interfeisā</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-5599">**ErrorText** - error text shown in the UI</span></span>

### <a name="officetelemetryvolumetrackingdata"></a><span data-ttu-id="8df23-6428">Office.Telemetry.VolumeTrackingData</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-6428">Office.Telemetry.VolumeTrackingData</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-6429">Notikumu apjoma izsekošanas metrika telemetrijas notikumiem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-6429">Event volume tracking metrics for telemetry events</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8df23-6430">Tiek apkopoti tālāk norādītie lauki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-6430">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-6431">**EventThreshold** — maksimālais viena notikuma instanču skaits, ko var nosūtīt laika periodā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-6431">**EventThreshold** - The maximum number of instances of a single event that can be sent in a window of time.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-6432">**HighestEventCount** — lielākais viena notikuma instanču skaits, kas nosūtīts šajā periodā.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-6432">**HighestEventCount** - The highest number of instances of a single event sent this window.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-6433">**HighestEventName** — notikuma ar vislielāko instanču skaitu šajā periodā nosaukums.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-6433">**HighestEventName** - The name of the event with the highest number of instances in this window.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-6434">**TimeWindowInSeconds** — perioda ilgums sekundēs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-6434">**TimeWindowInSeconds** - The duration of the window in seconds.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-6435">**TotalEvents** — kopējais periodā nosūtītais notikumu skaits.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-6435">**TotalEvents** - The total number of events sent during the window.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="8df23-6436">**UniqueEvents** — periodā nosūtīto unikālo notikumu skaits.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8df23-6436">**UniqueEvents** - The number of unique events sent during a window.</span></span>
